   20: 
   21: -module(ct_cth_update_result_post_end_tc_SUITE).
   22: 
   23: -compile(export_all).
   24: 
   25: -include("ct.hrl").
   26: 
   27: suite() ->
   28:     [{timetrap,{seconds,3}}].
   29: 
   30: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   31:     Config.
   32: 
   33: end_per_suite(Config) ->
   34:     ok.
   35: 
   36: init_per_group(_,Config) ->
   37:     Config.
   38: 
   39: end_per_group(_,_) ->
   40:     ok.
   41: 
   42: init_per_testcase(_,Config) ->
   43:     Config.
   44: 
   45: end_per_testcase(EndTimetrap,_) when EndTimetrap==end_timetrap_to_fail;
   46:                                      EndTimetrap==end_timetrap_to_skip->
   47:     timer:sleep(10000);
   48: end_per_testcase(EndFail,_) when EndFail==end_fail_to_fail;
   49:                                  EndFail==end_fail_to_skip->
   50:     ct:fail("change result when end fails");
   51: end_per_testcase(_,_) ->
   52:     ok.
   53: 
   54: all() ->
   55:     [tc_ok_to_fail,
   56:      tc_ok_to_skip,
   57:      tc_fail_to_ok,
   58:      tc_fail_to_skip,
   59:      tc_timetrap_to_ok,
   60:      tc_timetrap_to_skip,
   61:      tc_skip_to_fail,
   62:      end_fail_to_fail,
   63:      end_fail_to_skip,
   64:      end_timetrap_to_fail,
   65:      end_timetrap_to_skip].
   66: 
   67: %% Test cases starts here.
   68: tc_ok_to_fail(_Config) ->
   69:     ok.
   70: 
   71: tc_ok_to_skip(_Config) ->
   72:     ok.
   73: 
   74: tc_fail_to_ok(_Config) ->
   75:     ct:fail("should be changed to ok").
   76: 
   77: tc_fail_to_skip(_Config) ->
   78:     ct:fail("should be changed to skip").
   79: 
   80: tc_timetrap_to_ok(_Config) ->
   81:     timer:sleep(10000), % will time out after 3 sek
   82:     ok.
   83: 
   84: tc_timetrap_to_skip(_Config) ->
   85:     timer:sleep(10000), % will time out after 3 sek
   86:     ok.
   87: 
   88: tc_skip_to_fail(_Config) ->
   89:     {skip,"should be changed to fail"}.
   90: 
   91: end_fail_to_fail(_Config) ->
   92:     ok.
   93: 
   94: end_fail_to_skip(_Config) ->
   95:     ok.
   96: 
   97: end_timetrap_to_fail(_Config) ->
   98:     ok.
   99: 
  100: end_timetrap_to_skip(_Config) ->
  101:     ok.
